column5: When out fishing this morning, it was a nice day out on the lake. Not much bitting but fond this guy hagging around one of my holes usually  wally's around there but i don't mind i like pike as well. 25 inch not to bad for 4 hours on the lake
nice job brother, we tried on Scugog this afternoon with no Walley but a bunch of perch    Glad somebody knows how to catch em!  Thanks for sharing, MTBF
